# Architecture guardrails

Follow the canonical standard:

- Architecture & layer boundaries → [`agent-standards/10-architecture.md`](../../agent-standards/10-architecture.md)

Summary: Domain has no outward dependencies (no EF Core / ASP.NET); Application depends only on
Domain; Infrastructure implements abstractions; API is the composition root. Inject dependencies;
never `new` up infrastructure in business logic. If a change crosses a boundary, stop and explain.
